334
00:22:33.310 --> 00:22:34.310
Aren't you coming?

335
00:22:34.978 --> 00:22:37.314
I don't want to go in. Make it quick.

336
00:22:38.231 --> 00:22:40.317
Suit yourself. We'll be right back. okay?

337
00:22:42.319 --> 00:22:43.487
[woman] Kids. this way.

338
00:22:44.404 --> 00:22:45.530
Come this way. please.

339
00:22:47.908 --> 00:22:50.202
It's a children's room.
so it's a bit small.

340
00:22:50.285 --> 00:22:52.871
But it should be all right.
Please take your time.

341
00:22:52.954 --> 00:22:53.997
Thank you.

342
00:23:05.717 --> 00:23:07.719
