343
00:23:13.433 --> 00:23:16.395
[Gun-woo] <i>What do you think. Mom?
There's Woo-jin.</i>

344
00:23:16.937 --> 00:23:18.105
[Woo-jin] <i>Hello. ma'am.</i>

345
00:23:19.773 --> 00:23:20.774
