to such a powerful family.

355
00:23:44.548 --> 00:23:46.967
- And?
- And they got a video of the guy...

356
00:23:48.385 --> 00:23:51.096
But like... [sighs]

357
00:23:58.061 --> 00:24:01.148
[Mr. Oh] This is Kim Jun-min.
the sales director at Smile Capital.

358
00:24:01.231 --> 00:24:02.858
He has six priors for fraud.

359
00:24:03.608 --> 00:24:05.288
Used car fraud. credit card payment fraud.

360
00:24:05.944 --> 00:24:07.320
You name it. he's done it.

361
00:24:08.071 --> 00:24:10.991
Apparently. he served
at Seoul Nambu Detention Center.

362
00:24:11.992 --> 00:24:13.034
Im Jang-do.

363
00:24:13.118 --> 00:24:14.953
He was a cadet in training

364
00:24:15.495 --> 00:24:18.039
