401
00:25:57.889 --> 00:26:00.850
Thirty men without even using knives. Wow.

402
00:26:00.934 --> 00:26:01.935
Well. they're not your...

403
00:26:03.311 --> 00:26:06.940
Sir. it should be fine
if they move it early in the morning.

404
00:26:07.023 --> 00:26:08.567
Why don't you give them a chance?

405
00:26:09.150 --> 00:26:10.527
Hyeon-ju's a smart kid too.

406
00:26:17.075 --> 00:26:19.202
- [Gun-woo grunts]
- [Woo-jin] Okay. put it here.

407
00:26:19.286 --> 00:26:20.286
Ah. yes!

408
00:26:20.912 --> 00:26:21.912
Here.

409
00:26:22.956 --> 00:26:25.834
